function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 238') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.238!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') && (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '525fa026a33999cc748dea1d7f1e51f57269e104')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_7();
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '525fa026a33999cc748dea1d7f1e51f57269e104') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
}

if (is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') && (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != 'ebd6074fa13d88fdf08160db38ef668830806e2c')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_8();
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != 'ebd6074fa13d88fdf08160db38ef668830806e2c') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
}

if (is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') && (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '3105489679a3e0bf4886ed4ea9a41891c7029b18')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_9();

	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');

	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
}

if (is_file('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql') != 'b279496ac4d472ff0f9fa19e3cdee9c4f6532045')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/example_mssql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_10();
if (!is_file('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/sql/example_mssql.sql');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql') != 'b279496ac4d472ff0f9fa19e3cdee9c4f6532045') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/example_mssql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/example_mssql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/example_mssql.sql');
}

if (is_file('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql') != '1218f473a106f1f220a8b3bce06b21856383dd8a')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/example_mysql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_11();
if (!is_file('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/sql/example_mysql.sql');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql') != '1218f473a106f1f220a8b3bce06b21856383dd8a') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/example_mysql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/example_mysql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/example_mysql.sql');
}

	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/example_pgsql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/example_pgsql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/example_pgsql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);

		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}

}

if (is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql') != 'd742a20c69e2e19adefa97f77d6d71eca7fe31ee')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_16();

	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/wellknown_country_mssql.sql');
}

if (is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql') != 'ba30a5a4d5dfc95eaff1006ab35ac98d361e5ed5')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_17();
if (!is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql') != 'ba30a5a4d5dfc95eaff1006ab35ac98d361e5ed5') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/wellknown_country_mysql.sql');
}

	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_country_pgsql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_country_pgsql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}

	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/wellknown_country_pgsql.sql');
}

if (is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql') != 'ab7863e7375d6bee7e525a12519be5825905e9ef')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_19();
if (!is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql') != 'ab7863e7375d6bee7e525a12519be5825905e9ef') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/wellknown_other_mssql.sql');
}

if (is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql') && (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql') != '879ea03be12f77bc7ab0025b34cdf403820ad86a')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_20();
if (!is_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql') != '879ea03be12f77bc7ab0025b34cdf403820ad86a') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/sql/wellknown_other_mysql.sql');
}

	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/sql/wellknown_other_pgsql.sql');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/sql/wellknown_other_pgsql.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

}

if (!is_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
	writefile_22();
	if (!is_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php') != '7f412de2d5d9fc0633ff19fd2f8ff7d091931760') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/minify/src/CSS.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php') !== '7f412de2d5d9fc0633ff19fd2f8ff7d091931760') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php') !== 'f928182c924ab835bf68f15f6f4590ab08801861') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/minify/src/CSS.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/minify/src/CSS.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_22();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/minify/src/CSS.php') !== '7f412de2d5d9fc0633ff19fd2f8ff7d091931760') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/minify/src/CSS.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != 'f816fdf5b8bd6f3e4b621ed844b290e31b7f765b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'f816fdf5b8bd6f3e4b621ed844b290e31b7f765b') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '61098ffb7101c9f35f092b49d02023feb24ce6b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'f816fdf5b8bd6f3e4b621ed844b290e31b7f765b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '7ef29ac69a7330ad838e1772d09b7d9cc4a66c4c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '7ef29ac69a7330ad838e1772d09b7d9cc4a66c4c') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== 'c6b1041dc558634fbafdd0e49a0d6ff5098b2220') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '7ef29ac69a7330ad838e1772d09b7d9cc4a66c4c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	writefile_27();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') != '978e66a1d37903ff5e6d058520b6f852e84addd9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '978e66a1d37903ff5e6d058520b6f852e84addd9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '5f8d5d9fdf3a62406f5296dd62ecf361d5f56bea') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_27();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '978e66a1d37903ff5e6d058520b6f852e84addd9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
	writefile_28();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php') != '22f43d6dd7037ffe0981a063fa4170fc73589bf6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php') !== '22f43d6dd7037ffe0981a063fa4170fc73589bf6') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php') !== '4834d8fbd16c16fe2e5d8f340ed1cae8919b74fe') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php') !== '22f43d6dd7037ffe0981a063fa4170fc73589bf6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDataBasePlugin.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') != 'd9039e109e201b0a589f26a02ad1524f16847571') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== 'd9039e109e201b0a589f26a02ad1524f16847571') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== '7fcce7bb95dc9853a544ee1a00a989d73aa34097') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== 'd9039e109e201b0a589f26a02ad1524f16847571') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');

	}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	writefile_30();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') != '0434ad14052671b39f8e4d5aa126602d950c59e5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '0434ad14052671b39f8e4d5aa126602d950c59e5') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '209aeaa48fca72d19c2bc379baf8124ce10dadfc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '0434ad14052671b39f8e4d5aa126602d950c59e5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
	writefile_31();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php') != '96d1ebb81f7449005f987b6f5dcc2d38e51c3794') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php') !== '96d1ebb81f7449005f987b6f5dcc2d38e51c3794') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php') !== '7362417c89774257c16efcf70708e429c4a73a95') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php') !== '96d1ebb81f7449005f987b6f5dcc2d38e51c3794') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusRA.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	}

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/xml_utils.inc.php');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/xml_utils.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('includes/xml_utils.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_32();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/xml_utils.inc.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') != 'd095fb0de6ce5297c68538befa373cf68589bed6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd095fb0de6ce5297c68538befa373cf68589bed6') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '41c43a77d4b238b02f16a3f6943f2f18149044c5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd095fb0de6ce5297c68538befa373cf68589bed6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_39();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') != '7d1e483634b852bc7b6707364c909e88ab5986d1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== '7d1e483634b852bc7b6707364c909e88ab5986d1') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== '8c7502b11858ece1f4682f27642b105b6874dcd4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_39();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== '7d1e483634b852bc7b6707364c909e88ab5986d1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	writefile_40();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') != 'b5ac64329ee1ccebb739d8df7d3c1972c944edaf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== 'b5ac64329ee1ccebb739d8df7d3c1972c944edaf') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== '481b161331fd8a8a931f69e26c8f3556c4d4720c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_40();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== 'b5ac64329ee1ccebb739d8df7d3c1972c944edaf') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_41();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') != '7e4d8cc90beca6a651df8a5f5d35e51bd2ba6875') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '7e4d8cc90beca6a651df8a5f5d35e51bd2ba6875') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '604f979cf696ce586b0c82b3b4ae804d44bfce38') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_41();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '7e4d8cc90beca6a651df8a5f5d35e51bd2ba6875') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	writefile_44();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') != '8c2ab653fdfa0aea863a452b9237830e185e2943') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '8c2ab653fdfa0aea863a452b9237830e185e2943') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '2b11c7d9e4fdfe92bb2a79270c02b132c07c9906') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_44();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '8c2ab653fdfa0aea863a452b9237830e185e2943') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') != '932f3a881fcd946fadaa1f9a218851907ddf7208') {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== '932f3a881fcd946fadaa1f9a218851907ddf7208') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {

		}
		writefile_45();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== '932f3a881fcd946fadaa1f9a218851907ddf7208') {

	writefile_46();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') != 'baeda1786c15444ea4e382ad0ad8d7fbfe14746d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== 'baeda1786c15444ea4e382ad0ad8d7fbfe14746d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '5826bd011ee84a050d429c813d838d513cf16c3f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_46();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== 'baeda1786c15444ea4e382ad0ad8d7fbfe14746d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_47();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') != 'eb770004c5308a618a8b220da440fc83abe9822f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== 'eb770004c5308a618a8b220da440fc83abe9822f') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== '3d517377167811d79e8617487bca8bdc3476b2d0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_47();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== 'eb770004c5308a618a8b220da440fc83abe9822f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	writefile_48();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') != '67bc74308c08a7347fa6098c2394b76da52d971e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '67bc74308c08a7347fa6098c2394b76da52d971e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '6b4b7a775be2cd9bac42b5747fff4e783fcd176a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '67bc74308c08a7347fa6098c2394b76da52d971e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_50();
	if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php') != 'ad3e36be9318d272af8e9223d267bc24a9c522a4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ad3e36be9318d272af8e9223d267bc24a9c522a4') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '3d0373eb53048dd301101394b955964baf8faeda') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ad3e36be9318d272af8e9223d267bc24a9c522a4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/099_object_log/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	writefile_53();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') != '40e31163a3ceb01a81db0248c98c94da33c6a98a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '40e31163a3ceb01a81db0248c98c94da33c6a98a') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== 'f23583791137d1821f4e8616901b9e2dfc8c9533') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '40e31163a3ceb01a81db0248c98c94da33c6a98a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	writefile_54();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != 'ffa3322dc251a327b170b88a13f7222bf2924e3d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'ffa3322dc251a327b170b88a13f7222bf2924e3d') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '72fdb173e3555f43ac3f98dc3fbaeed8c2e9e35d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'ffa3322dc251a327b170b88a13f7222bf2924e3d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_55();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != 'f6677cccfb00aa5936b358ccf2aa6d23b4114605') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'f6677cccfb00aa5936b358ccf2aa6d23b4114605') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '9aa6e28893eab2d96665dde73acec45d632b1a27') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'f6677cccfb00aa5936b358ccf2aa6d23b4114605') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/includes/http_class.class.php');
	writefile_59();
	if (!is_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/includes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php') != '28813cbc13a086cccee1de531366452cb6ad64ac') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/includes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/includes/http_class.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/includes/http_class.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php') !== '28813cbc13a086cccee1de531366452cb6ad64ac') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php') !== '8deca3825b208a95bf4a167037bbf2b35c77e9d4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/includes/http_class.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/includes/http_class.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/includes/http_class.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/includes/http_class.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_59();
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/http_class.class.php') !== '28813cbc13a086cccee1de531366452cb6ad64ac') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/includes/http_class.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
	writefile_60();
	if (!is_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php') != 'f03ca65738ba8e48cfb7cf075d52b990ad606dc0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php') !== 'f03ca65738ba8e48cfb7cf075d52b990ad606dc0') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php') !== '36dc980c8ace43a1a6179ec1d8112dfb349f8412') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_60();
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php') !== 'f03ca65738ba8e48cfb7cf075d52b990ad606dc0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/includes/vnag_framework.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: update/index.php

if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/index.php');
	writefile_61();
	if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/index.php') != 'bdf6c7e6f1cd5afd96a81e225c82675a8447bcfb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'bdf6c7e6f1cd5afd96a81e225c82675a8447bcfb') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '83ce81cc060fd5268a12d862811039f4a69f8d61') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_61();
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'bdf6c7e6f1cd5afd96a81e225c82675a8447bcfb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
		}
	}
}
